amendatorysection.chaptername: State University, State Colleges, and Postsecondary Education
amendatorysection.catchline: Wayne State College; Legislative intent to appropriate funds for cooperative programs.
amendatorysection.para: It is the intent of the Legislature to appropriate fifty thousand dollars for fiscal year 2022-23 from the General Fund to the Board of Trustees of the Nebraska State Colleges for cooperative programs with Wayne State College.
